ritual:
name: Visual Studio Code installation ritual
date: 2025-11
environment: Windows 11 (Parallels virtual environment)
source: https://code.visualstudio.com/
actions:
- Run the exe file and complete the installation
- Enable the Add to PATH option
- Enable the Open with Code option
- Launch confirmed, select the "Dark+" theme
perspective: Microsoft provides the development environment, and Display Authority accepts and records it
